fields.field: Σδ integrator capacitance. Value should be >39pF and <180pF. C0G, 10%, >6.3V, AEC-Q200.

Forms Σδ integrator. Nearly all pin-compatible opamps will do. Ensure >80dB open loop gain, <1pA/rtHz current noise, supply voltage down to at least 4.5V and up to at least 5.5V and rail-to-rail operation. Voltage noise non-critical.
